OL,3,CInquest into death of man shot in
OL,4,Cpolice station car park to be heard
OL,5,Cnext year
OL,7,FAn inquest into the death of a man who
OL,8,Fwas shot in a police station car park
OL,9,Fwill be heard by a jury next year.
OL,11,FIn a short hearing at Derby Coroner's
OL,12,FCourt on Tuesday, assistant coroner
OL,13,FSabyta Kaushal said that 23 witnesses
OL,14,Fwill be called upon to give evidence
OL,15,Fat an inquest into the death of Marius
OL,16,FCiolac, which is expected to last four
OL,17,Fweeks.
