OL,7,FShe told the court that a provisional
OL,8,Finquest date had been fixed for
OL,9,FJanuary 21 next year and the evidence
OL,10,Fwill be heard in front of a jury.
OL,12,FThe Independent Office for Police
OL,13,FConduct (IOPC) previously said that Mr
OL,14,FCiolac, 35, died from a single gunshot
OL,15,Fwound to the abdomen after a police
OL,16,Fissue firearm was discharged at Ascot
OL,17,FDrive police station in Derby on
OL,18,FOctober 7 2022.
