OL,7,FA multi-bang stun grenade, a baton
OL,8,Fround and a Taser had been used by
OL,9,Fofficers to try to stop the 35-year-
OL,10,Fold Romanian national after reports
OL,11,Fthat windows had been smashed and a
OL,12,Fman had been seen with a knife.
OL,14,FThe firearm was discharged at about
OL,15,F10.03am. Mr Ciolac, from Osmaston Road
OL,16,Fin Derby, was taken to hospital, where
OL,17,Fhe died later that morning.
OL,19,FThe IOPC said three knives of various
OL,20,Fsizes were recovered from the scene.
