OL,7,FMs Kaushal told the hearing: "The
OL,8,Ffamily are anxious to move the case
OL,9,Fon, we are looking at a case that
OL,10,Fhappened near the end of 2022.
OL,12,F"They would like to progress matters."
OL,14,FMr Ciolac's family attended the pre-
OL,15,Finquest hearing remotely, using a
OL,16,FRomanian interpreter, and were told
OL,17,Fthat "core evidence" from CCTV and
OL,18,Fbody-worn camera footage has been
OL,19,Fshared with the interested persons in
OL,20,Fthe case.
